      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Here are three Instagram caption options to announce your new diversity and equity initiatives:\n\n**Option 1 (Excited & Forward-Looking):**\nWe are thrilled to announce a bold new chapter for our boutique! 🌟 Starting today, we are actively redefining our hiring practices and shop displays to center diverse voices and authentic representation. We believe that true community thrives when everyone feels seen, valued, and empowered to be their best selves. Thank you for supporting our commitment to building a more inclusive future! #CommunityFirst #InclusiveFashion #EquityInAction\n\n**Option 2 (Warm & Personable):**\nHey friends! 👋 We want our shop to be a true reflection of the amazing world we live in. That's why we are launching new diversity and equity initiatives in our hiring and store layout right now. This isn't just a trend; it's a necessary step toward creating a space where everyone belongs. We are so grateful for your support as we build a more authentic and welcoming environment for all of you. Let's celebrate difference together! #Authenticity #ShopLocal #DiversityMatters\n\n**Option 3 (Short & Action-Oriented):**\nIt's time to do better.",
