      "content": "thanks. i like the second one, but honestly option 3 feels a bit heavy? like \"it's time to do better\" sounds kind of like we're admitting we were doing something wrong or being bad before. can you give me a few more that focus more on the benefits of having a more diverse team and display, maybe something that sounds more positive and less like a lecture?",
